{With your 12 point hand you need to force to game. It would also be nice to find out if partner has a 4-card \H suit. So you cue-bid 3\S. This is the lebensohl version of Stayman, but WITH NO \S STOPPER. (Direct Denies)

Partner says 4\H and you pass.}

